Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ホワイト  ブラック
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:59.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,White Black
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:09.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,さぁ  お遊びは終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:09.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,好了 遊戲結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,ブラック！ホワイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,Black！White！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:14.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:14.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保倫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,力を合わせるポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,將力量結合起來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,漲る勇気
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,昂揚之勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,溢れる希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,滿溢之希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光り輝く絆とともに！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,攜光輝璀璨之羈絆 結合與共！
